text: Shah Newaz is a Communist Party of Bangladesh politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jamalpur-4. ==Career== Newaz was elected to parliament from Jamalpur-4 as a Communist Party of Bangladesh candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Communist Party of Bangladesh politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Shah Newaz
